Class MultiMediaManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.jingleold.media.JingleMediaManager

  • public class MultiMediaManager
extends JingleMediaManager
    Implements a MultiMediaManager using other JingleMediaManager implementations. It supports every Codecs that JingleMediaManagers added has.
